name: logger
description: Logger method that takes in YUIDoc warnings array and checks those warnings against special features that we support. This allows us to use special tags for Ember apps, and still support logging for incorrect tags, but suppress warnings for unknown tags we have added

params.name: options
params.description: Contains logger options and data to handle

props.name: warnings
props.description: YUIDoc generated warnings array of type: `{ message, line }`

props.name: whiteListTags
props.description: Tags whitelisted for support in Ember Fountainhead
